            <p>Hey There 🫶 I'm Giorgia, a 26-year-old Italian 🤌 who has called Malta 🇲🇹 home since 2016. My professional journey began in iGaming, where I honed my expertise in customer service and digital marketing, mastering skills such as <strong>SEO</strong>, <strong>website optimization</strong>, and <strong>strategic planning.</strong>
