            Visit my <a href="https://www.giorgiacorsetti.com" class="plain-link">creative portfolio</a> if you're curious to know what I achieved!
            Beyond my professional pursuits, I absolutely love <u>painting</u> 🎨, <u>drawing</u> ✏️, <u>gardening</u> 🪴 and delving into <u>psychology books</u> 📚 during my free time. I also like to be involved in voluntary initiatives related to mental health support, environmental restoration, and preservation. Nature holds a special place in my heart and I often find peace in walks, considering it a therapeutic escape from the distractions of society.
            Now equipped with a wealth of knowledge from these courses, I am eager to showcase my skills and contribute remotely. Let's connect and explore the possibilities of collaboration!💜💜💜💜💜</p>
